metadata.name: Me as a tiger
metadata.description:
I painted half of my face as a tiger because the tiger symbolizes the ultimate meaning of strength, will, personal power and courage.
A shadow or part of you that you normally try to hide or deny. The tiger is also a symbol of
Aggression or anger directed at you or towards someone.
unpredictability in life, actions or feelings;
In the field of symbolism, the tiger is associated with positive and negative meanings.
